About the game and the &quot;find group&quot; problem. I'd like to point out to the original poster a question. How about your guild ? I think most high lvl don't make anymore pickup group but more guild group. I'd say try to build guild group, you'll have better time and experience. And since they will know you for long they will remember fun stories that you will make you able to smile about during long med break or raid prep sessions.<br>
My best time with group for the moment is Me and a druid, we duo a lot and when a guild teamate is lfg for long we take it so he has fun with us. Maybe an immediate solution for you. Find another soloer in your guild and try to work out strategies. I personnally hate to solo, if I have to I will log my alt monk and wait for a guild call (and my monk don't lvl fast).<br>
